As a Shen OTP of the original one i loved the old one and was finally starting to warm up to the new Shen then he just got his damage in the early game gutted, i can't even play him anymore he feels so bad the rework was a mistake and the buffs were a mistake.

Riot even said they didn't think it worked out in one of their posts.

